# Hearthstone APIs

# Group User
User related resources of the **User API**

## Signup [/user/signup]
Create a user.

### Signup a user [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

        {
            name: "tim",
            pass: "123",
            email: "tang.jilong@gmail.com",
            avatar: "",
            deviceToken: "abc123"
        }

+ Response Success (application/json)

        {
            success: true,
            msg: 'Signup sucess!'
        }

+ Response Failure (application/json)

        {
            success: false,
            msg: 'User name must be 0-9,a-z,A-Z',
            name: 'tim',
            email:'tang.jilong@gmail.com'
        }        

+ Response Failure (application/json)

        {
            success: false,
            msg: 'User Name has been used.',
            name: 'tim',
            email:'tang.jilong@gmail.com'
        }        

+ Response Failure (application/json)

        {
            success: false,
            msg: 'Invalid email address.',
            name: 'tim',
            email:'tang.jilong@gmail.com'
        }        


+ Response Failure (application/json)

        {
            success: false,
            msg: 'Incomplete user info.',
            name: 'tim',
            email:'tang.jilong@gmail.com'
        }        

